title: Debian 12.1 “Bookworm” Released with 89 Bug Fixes and 26 Security Updates
description:
Debian GNU/Linux 12.1 is now available for download as the first point release in the Debian GNU/Linux 12 “Bookworm” series adding 102 security updates and 92 miscellaneous bug fixes.
